Michael NOWICKI, Petitioner,
v.
BOARD OF TRUSTEES, Police and Firemen's Retirement System, Respondent. C-476 September Term 2018
081795 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 18, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002966-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
